#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_tables.rst:23
msgid "The attribute table item"
msgstr "Položka atributové tabulky"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_tables.rst:25
msgid ""
"Any layer in the project can have its attributes shown in the print layout. "
"Use the |addTable| :guilabel:`Add Attribute Table` tool following "
":ref:`items creation instructions <create_layout_item>` to add a new table "
"item that you can later manipulate the same way as exposed in "
":ref:`interact_layout_item`."
msgstr ""
"Atributy z jakékoliv vrstvy v projektu mohou být zobrazeny v náhledu pro "
"tisk."

